@jbonofre I pinged you on Slack as well, but this PR is actually what it's about.
@dhalperi and I were trying to [configure](https://builds.apache.org/view/Beam/job/beam_PostCommit_RunnableOnService_SparkLocal/configure) Jenkins to run ROS-SparkRunner for this PR branch because that seems to be the only way to test if this branch achieved it's goal - to allow enough retries for Spark to find ports so it could execute ROS.
Any ideas who has permissions for that ? Thanks!
